song_lyrics: Chālo chālo Jiraṇgaḍh jaīe re, Swāmī pragaṭyā chhe
Karī darshan sukhiyā thaīe re... Swāmī 1
Mūḷ Akshar pūraṇ kām re... Swāmī
Thaī rahyo chhe Brahma killol re... Swāmī 3
